        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-递归"><a href="#1-递归" class="headerlink" title="1.递归"></a>1.递归</h2><ol><li><p>三个本质属性</p><ul><li>递归模式</li><li>终止条件</li><li>变化</li></ul></li><li><p>步骤</p><ul><li>确定问题的参数</li><li>使用参数表示解</li><li>在解简单明了的情况下确定简单情景</li><li>确定复杂情景与简单情景的关系</li></ul></li></ol><h3 id="1-1在限制条件下选取小球"><a href="#1-1在限制条件下选取小球" class="headerlink" title="1.1在限制条件下选取小球"></a>1.1在限制条件下选取小球</h3><blockquote><p>双色球问题：</p><p>在一个袋子里有无数个红球(R)和蓝球(B),玩家需要选取n个小球，但是不能连续选取两个红球;而且需要考虑选取顺序:选取红蓝(RB)跟蓝红( BR)是两种不同的情况。问:有多少种不同的选取方法?这个问题可以利用递归解决，采用上述的四个步骤:</p><ol><li><p>确定问题的参数</p><p>在这个问题中参数是小球的数目n</p></li><li><p>使用参数表示解</p><p>假设f(n)为解：表示在不能连续选取两个红球的情况下，选取n个小球的方案数</p></li><li><p>在解简单明了的情况下确定简单情景</p><p>如果只选取1个小球的话，只有两种可能: R或者B。因此，f(n)为2。如果选取<br>2个小球，则有三种可能: RB、BR和B。因此，f(n)为3。</p></li><li><p>确定复杂情景与简单情景的关系</p><p>如果选取n个小球(n&gt; 2)，则第一个小球可以是R，也可以是B。因此，第一个<br>小球有两种可能。<br>(1)如果第一个小球是B，那么剩余的n-1个小球必须遵守同样的规则:不能连续<br>选取两个红球。共有f(n-1)种可能。<br>(2)如果第一个小球是R，那么第二个小球必须是B。第二个小球是蓝球使得第三，个小球既可以是R也可以是B，没有任何限制。因此，剩余的n-2个小球必须遵守同样的规则，共有f(n-2)中可能</p></li></ol><p>由此分析：f(n)便是f(n-1)和f(n-2)的和</p><p> <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128123822.png" alt="image-20210128123822504"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128132245.png" alt="image-20210128132245351"></p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> 双色球问题 <span class="token punctuation">{</span>   <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>       System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>   <span class="token punctuation">}</span>   <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/*   如果第一个求是红球，则第二个球只能是篮球,第三个求没有要求所以剩下的n-2个球有f(n-2)种   如果第一个求是篮球,则第二个球没有要求，所以剩下的n-1个球有f(n-1)种    */</span>   <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>       <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>           <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>       <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>           <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>       <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>   <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre></blockquote><blockquote><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128132919.png" alt="image-20210128132919687"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128132951.png" alt="image-20210128132950957"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128133028.png" alt="image-20210128133028651"></p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> 三色球问题 <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/*    第一个球是蓝球,则第二个球没有要求，则剩下的n-1个球有f(n-1)种    第一个球是绿球,则第二个球没有要求，则剩下的n-1个球有f(n-1)种    第一个球是红球        第二个球是蓝球,第三个球没有要求,则剩下的n-2个球有f(n-2)种        第二个球是绿球,第三个球没有要求,则剩下的n-2个球有f(n-2)种     */</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">8</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre></blockquote><blockquote><p>三色球附加问题</p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//在一个袋子里有无数个红球(R)和蓝球(B),绿球(G)玩家需要选取n个小球，但是不能连续选取两个红球或两个绿球;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 而且需要考虑选取顺序:选取红蓝(RB)跟蓝红( BR)是两种不同的情况。问:有多少种不同的选取方法</span></code></pre><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> 三色球附加限制条件 <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">g</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//表示第一个球是绿球,选取n个小球的解</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">b</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">r</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">b</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//表示第一个球是蓝球,选取n个小球的解</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">r</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">b</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">g</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//=>f(n-1)</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">r</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//表示第一个球是红球,选取n个小球的解</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">g</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">b</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//表示选取n个球的解</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">7</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">b</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">r</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">g</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre></blockquote><h3 id="1-2单行道"><a href="#1-2单行道" class="headerlink" title="1.2单行道"></a>1.2单行道</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128143151.png" alt="image-20210128143151306"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128143220.png" alt="image-20210128143219996"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128143305.png" alt="image-20210128143305765"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128143344.png" alt="image-20210128143344838"></p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> 单行道 <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/*    车只能向北和向东行驶    A(x1,y1)  B(x2,y2)    1. x = x2-x1  y=y2-y1    2. f(x,y)表示从原点(x1,x2)到终点(x2,y2)有多少条路径    3. 当x&lt;0,说明B在A的西边,无解       当y&lt;0,说明B在A的南边,无解       当x=0,说明在同一列,只能一直向北       当y=0,说明在同一行,只能一直向东     4. 当x>0 &amp;&amp; y>0时,可以向北也可以向东        向北x不变,y-1        向东y不变,x-1     5. 当x=0 &amp;&amp; y=0定义为一种解     */</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> x<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> y<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token number">0</span> <span class="token operator">||</span> y<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">0</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span> y<span class="token operator">>=</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>y<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">0</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span> x<span class="token operator">>=</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><h3 id="1-3汉罗塔"><a href="#1-3汉罗塔" class="headerlink" title="1.3汉罗塔"></a>1.3汉罗塔</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128150311.png" alt="image-20210128150311713"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128150337.png" alt="image-20210128150337497"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128150400.png" alt="image-20210128150359962"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128150442.png" alt="image-20210128150442769"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128150501.png" alt="image-20210128150501570"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128150526.png" alt="image-20210128150526572"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/17998/BlogImages/master/img/20210128150602.png" alt="image-20210128150602105"></p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> 汉诺塔 <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/*    f(n)表示将n个圆盘从A移动到B共需要多少步    A->B,A->C,B->性质一样    思路：        1. 先将上面的n-1个圆盘从A移动到C需要f(n-1)        2. 再将最下面的圆盘从A移动到B需要1步        3. 最后将C上面的圆盘移动到B需要f(n-1)步     */</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">f</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><h3 id="1-4计算整数分拆"><a href="#1-4计算整数分拆" class="headerlink" title="1.4计算整数分拆"></a>1.4计算整数分拆</h3><h4 id="1-4-1计算“1”的个数"><a href="#1-4-1计算“1”的个数" class="headerlink" title="1.4.1计算“1”的个数"></a>1.4.1计算“1”的个数</h4><h4 id="1-4-2仅使用奇数进行拆分"><a href="#1-4-2仅使用奇数进行拆分" class="headerlink" title="1.4.2仅使用奇数进行拆分"></a>1.4.2仅使用奇数进行拆分</h4><h4 id="1-4-3使用递增数进行拆分"><a href="#1-4-3使用递增数进行拆分" class="headerlink" title="1.4.3使用递增数进行拆分"></a>1.4.3使用递增数进行拆分</h4><h4 id="1-4-4交替使用奇偶数进行拆分"><a href="#1-4-4交替使用奇偶数进行拆分" class="headerlink" title="1.4.4交替使用奇偶数进行拆分"></a>1.4.4交替使用奇偶数进行拆分</h4><h3 id="1-4-5整数分拆问题的推广"><a href="#1-4-5整数分拆问题的推广" class="headerlink" title="1.4.5整数分拆问题的推广"></a>1.4.5整数分拆问题的推广</h3><h3 id="1-4-6解决分拆问题的错误方法"><a href="#1-4-6解决分拆问题的错误方法" class="headerlink" title="1.4.6解决分拆问题的错误方法"></a>1.4.6解决分拆问题的错误方法</h3>]]></content>
      
      
